WEBVTT

00:42.165 --> 00:45.584
Out of tune they are going.

00:45.609 --> 00:50.131
They are going out of tune a little bit.
Let them go in tune, you see?

00:50.156 --> 00:55.598
One should not go in…speak with heart,
and speak with feelings,

00:55.623 --> 01:03.559
